        <abstract> 
<p>Asks what position the sub-peduncles assume when the main flower peduncle of <hi rend="italic">Oxalis</hi> is tied so as to be horizontal.</p> 
            <p>Asks whether FD can find some plants at Kew for CD to trace epinastic and hyponastic movements.</p>
